<D>__{you leave kyle here. with us. until he finishes high school.}
<C>__{cindy}
<D>__{i'm his mother. he belongs with me.}
<C>__{mike}
<D>__{are you sure he feels that way?}
<C>__{cindy}
<D>__{don't tell me what my son feels! he's coming with me and there isn't anything you can do about that.}
